  <brief_title>The Treatment of Insomnia in Patients With HIV Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Doxepin and Temazepam in HIV Seropositive Patients With Insomnia.</official_title>
